<br>
My opinion: Because the cleric epic is essentially different then any other epics in game. All the other epics for all the other classes are fine weapons indeed, but the cleric epic isn't a weapon at all. It's a force multiplier for guilds in that it allows a guild to recover from a failed engagement in a few minutes versus an hour or so. In that, more attempts on mob X can be made in less time, more successes on mob X can be scored, and more Lewtz X's for the guild as a whole.<br>
<br>
